    "body": "Thanks a lot for the report @merikonjatta, I can confirm this.\r\n\r\nNote for ourselves: the problem is that the global flags are not being propagated to the sub-processes:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/blob/6f291668d5791bf7a3471f465a93326931e4282c/packages/hardhat-core/src/builtin-tasks/test.ts#L90\r\n\r\nI wonder if this should be fixed in the core of hardhat instead of the built-in task. That is, maybe Hardhat should have an invariant that, if you can configure something with the environment variable X, then that envvar X will be set in after the runtime is initialized. @alcuadrado thoughts?",
